Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Are those sweet...\Ncarrot pancakes I smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... How divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The aroma... spiced warm apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. And the smell of... smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke? Smoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,SMOOOUUARGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've ruined the surprise.\NI was gonna serve you breakfast in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, g'mornin', Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that\NSweetie Belle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...cooked this yummy lookin'\Nbreakfast all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could burn juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been giving her lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if she's\Ngot a cutie mark in fancy cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the time we get back\Nfrom our vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacation? Is that this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As in... starting-this-very-instant this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. Apple sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have the bestest time\Ntwo sisters could even have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go grab my stuff\Nfrom dad's wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So... now when you say "a week"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... seven whole days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And six night, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a short time to spend\Nwith your lil' sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got such a long to-do list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I suppose\N"spend time with your sister"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...will just have to\Nbe added to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's get that\Nkitchen all cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaned up? But we\Nhaven't even eaten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the gesture, but we simply\Ncan't eat *this* breakfast. It's burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, my dear.\NI'll get a proper breakfast going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Uh, in one moment,\NSweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just get things started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said I was gonna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are! You... can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...put the garnish on the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this parsley?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay now, easy! It has to be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful! Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for perfection here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things I must attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take the dirty towels\Nto the laundry room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! I'll make myself useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'd make\Nmyself useful. Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You washed my incredibly expensive\None of a kind designer crochet wool sweater!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how hard\Nthese things are to come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The big deal is that\Nin the heat of the sun wool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...shrinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I must create.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Stay out of trouble, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to do something\Nnice for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,RAAAGH! I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When is Rarity gonna finish her work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stay out of trouble, okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got in trouble for drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. This needs something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a special drawing for y...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Did you use these gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have more\Nin your work room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu... but these are extremely\Nrare baby blue sapphires!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need them for an outfit for\Nan extremely important client!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle. What am I\Ngoing to do with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! We could paint together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We could ride bikes, play chess,\Nsing a song, catch frogs, pillow fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have to go and find\Nsome more of these gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you and help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can help by picking up\Nthese papers and stacking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Neatly. Put the pens and pencils\Nexactly where you've found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And please find something to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...that doesn't create\Na large mess for me to clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez Louise, can't I do anything right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My inspiration room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT DID YOU DO?!\NWHAT DID YOU DO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the big mess in your room,\NI thought I'd clean it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't a mess!\NIt was organized chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about finished\Nplanning my new fashion line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and you... you...\Nyou went and... and then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you put everything away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time I make\Na mess, you get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was MY mess.\NIn MY house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'll have to\Nstart from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I... I thought it would...\Nmake you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,HAPPY?! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the sleepover at Rarity's goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's smashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish we could do\Nsomething special together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...that didn't include me\Ngoofing anything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The Sisterhooves Social!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack and I do it every year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Rarity could compete against other\Nsister teams in all these neat events.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like the perfect\Nway for us to hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity will think it's an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a ridiculous idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A contest at Sweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...very clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? Now you're back\Nto hating messes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle! Watch your tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am still your big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! And any sister, who\Ncares about her sister, goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle! Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing silly little games\Nin the dirt is just... uncouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With or without a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe I'll try the Sisterhooves\NSocial without a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think I'll try the rest\Nof my life without a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm the one who's\Nruining your life!? Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you looked around this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who would be\Nbetter off with no sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like we\Nfinally agree on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us needs a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,DEAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,DEAL! GOODBYE, UNSISTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uncouth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the Sisterhooves\NSocial was uncouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Uncouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What's uncouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the social.\NShe thinks I'm uncouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, Rarity thinks\Neverything's uncouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's uncouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It means uncivil.\NYou know, bad mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, just give Rarity some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll come around. Sisters always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sisters like Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now. Apple Bloom and I\Ngot some chores to finish up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you want me to help?\NI just mess everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. That's just\Nstinkin'-thinkin'. Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good catch there, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a chore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we can't sell\Nthe bruised apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...we gotta collect them all\Nfor the pigs to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lotta work.\NSo we make a game of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It is hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity never wants to do chores together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All that work ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. It's usually a big mess in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,IDEA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall call it:\N"Full Spectrum Fashions".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if Sweetie Belle hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She still shouldn't have touched\Nmy things without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! You're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making grape juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity would call\Nthe fashion police on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I got grape juice anywhere\N*near* her precious outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Applejack! She didn't mea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'you like them grapes,\Nyou little whippersnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to get these fabrics washed\Nfor my fabulous new line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! My favorite sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe that Sweetie Belle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Opal, Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if Sweetie Belle knew\Nthe sweater was perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sweetie Belle should consider\Nherself perfectly lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...that this thoughtless\Nmishap turned out all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's as if they're just one pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,YEEHAW!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to corral some critters, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity never high-hooves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more and this ensemble is fini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's her silly little\Narts and crafts project?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sweetie Belle!\NMy one and only sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time I could have\Nspent with you was wasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...complaining and wishing\Nyou were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,WOE IS ME!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I must get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As Celestia is my witness,\NI shall never be sisterless again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been galloping all over,\Nlooking for you. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, unsister.\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Better be careful. You might\Nget some dust on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sweetie Belle. I want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not better off without a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not better off\Nwithout a sister either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending the day with Applejack and\NApple Bloom made me realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh, Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how happy\NI am to hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm adopting\NApplejack as my big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A sister is someone who loves\Nand takes care of another sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack's a real sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Sweetie Belle.\NDon't get ahead of yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she's MY big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she should be *your* sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...so she could teach you what\Na good sister is supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, actually I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't need lessons on being\Na good sister. I... I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'll show you how to\Ncook my favorite quiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... or I'll show you the proper\Nway to beautify your mane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't that be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to go home with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...so *we* can do what *you* wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still sisters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that apology went swimmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, why do you have to be\Nso good and make me look so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again you're\Nthinkin' about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bein' sisters is a give and take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doin'\Na whole lotta takin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you haven't been\Ndoin' a whole lotta givin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I give lessons. Reasonable demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bein' sisters is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...apple pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have amazin' apples and you can\Nhave a wonderfully crispy crust...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but only together can you\Nhave a perfect apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But apart all we are is just a pile\Nof mush and some crumbly dry mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope it isn't too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's a good\Nthing Rarity isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I see "uncouth" written\Nall over this contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the size of that pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last word Rarity would use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh my! What a repulsive monstrosity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"This thing needs\Na head to toe makeover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you two have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wish I had a sister\Nto run a race with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,AB and I figured since\Nwe do this every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd like you borrow my sis,\Nso you can give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this thing is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a...? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Confangled modern doohickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the event you all\Nbeen waitin' for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sistersoci... The Socialhoof...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dagnabit! You know, the big race!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have five teams\Nthis year for the event!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So all ya head on up\Nto the finish line, y'hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,THE START LINE! You coulda said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Day. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And may the best sisters win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On your mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,GOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Applejack. You were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even care that we didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Where's Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We switched places over\Nat the very first mudhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did the whole\Ncompetition together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That we did, little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, except for the start line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you finished together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you were all in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Us. I did it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? We *are* apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I think we\Ndeserve a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The spa, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. What should we\Nwrite to the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Having a sister is just about\Nthe bestest thing in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"But it sure isn't the easiest."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I agree, that being sisters\Nis a wonderful thing..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"...but it takes teamwork."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sometimes it's about compromising."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sometimes it's about accepting\Neach other's differences."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"But mostly it's about\Nhaving fun together."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even if it means getting your\Nhooves a little bit dirty."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-A lo...\N-Hold it, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about... "a medium\Namount of dirty..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"...not too little, not\Ntoo much, just right."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
